title: Dan Kennedy photographs Richard Madden
description:
Will he or won’t he be the next James Bond? Internet speculation is rife! But actor Richard Madden (who you may recognise from his Sunday night pants on tight role in The Bodyguard, or in his depiction of doomed Robb Stark in Game of Thrones). 

Either way, he is force to be reckoned with!

He was photographed at Loft Studios  by Dan Kennedy for the Sunday Times. Whether he takes the 007 crown or not, you can definitely check him out in his next role, as John Reid, Elton John’s manager and first boyfriend, in the upcoming film Rocketman about the singer’s rise to fame.

The BTS video is from Dan Kennedy’s photography Facebook page.

Read the full feature here

https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/richard-madden-interview-bodyguard-game-of-thrones-and-why-he-doesnt-think-hesa-sex-symbol-jztwg0np5

By Sara Darling

25.10

blog.title: Alle.
blog.description:
librisognierealta.it è il mio blog.
Ho sempre sentito il bisogno di averne uno, ma non avevo mai trovato un argomento che mi spingesse a continuare a scrivere, finché non ho abbracciato la mia natura ossessia-compulsiva e assolutamente pignola! Da questo è nato il mio blog di recensioni e scleri di vario genere: Libri, Sogni e Realtà.

summary: Curiosità: Game of Thrones - Libro Secondo
title: Curiosità: Game of Thrones - Libro Secondo
body:
Curiosità: Game of Thrones – Libro Secondo

Curiosità: Game of Thrones – Libro Secondo

Il secondo libro delle Cronache del ghiaccio e del fuoco di R.R. Martin è stato pubblicato nel 1999 con il titolo di Lo scontro dei Re. Contiene anche questo due volumi, Il regno dei lupi e La regna dei draghi arrivati entrambi nel 2001.

Nel 2011 la HBO ha creato la trasposizione televisiva della serie ed è per questo che ci troviamo qui in questo…

summary: I love how Jorah tells Daenerys that the Dothraki will only respect her if she proves herself strong... AFTER she got into Qarth...
body: I love how Jorah tells Daenerys that the Dothraki will only respect her if she proves herself strong… AFTER she got into Qarth by threatening to kill its rulers, AFTER she burned half her enemies there to death and condemned the rest to a slow, torturous death by starvation, AFTER she left the town laden with riches. Looks pretty fucking strong to me. What have YOU done recently, my good Ser?

title: Lone walf die ...
body:

‘’lone wolf dies and the pack survives’’

His both daughter is in capital in this situation. but Ned said this words to Arya .  the most important words from Ned . Why GRRM  decided only Arya and not Sansa? 

We can recall. 
in this scene Ned talked with Arya. she had sword in her hand, which is gift of Jon
